    "Reconstruction sometimes integrates real-world physics and 3D geometry, offering more comprehensive item or scene attributes in comparison to rearrangement jobs.",
    "Realtime robots are using reconstruction techniques with high precision by utilizing the acquired depth dimension.",
    "Tasks and CVThree design categories may be used to group machine translation systems: direct, transfer-based, and interlingua-based systems.",
    "Fig 1 shows the famous \"Vauquois Triangle\" (VT), a common way to represent these three tactics.",
    "At the topmost level of the triangle is Interlingua machine translation, in the very center is transfer-based translation, and at the very bottom is direct translation, representing the three levels of hierarchical representation."
